 <metadata>
  <name>RTH - Prestwich Hills Via Sandy Lane</name>
  <desc>Exit through the park towards Bury New Road, crossing over and heading left towards Manchester. Turn right up Butterstile until you reach Sandy Lane then turn left. At the end of Sandy Lane turn left onto Hilton Lane then left at the top back on to Bury New Road. At Butterstile turn left again and then second left onto Prestwich Hills to re-group.  We will then do a few loops of Prestwich Hills in either direction before returning to the park via Butterstile / Bury New Road.</desc>
  <author>
   <name>Dale Richards</name>
   <link href="https://www.strava.com/athletes/108724580"/>
  </author>
  <copyright author="OpenStreetMap contributors">
   <year>2020</year>
   <license>https://www.openstreetmap.org/copyright</license>
  </copyright>
  <link href="https://www.strava.com/routes/3427672282158618974"/>
 </metadata>
